cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.ME, cs.LG, cs.CV 

This paper discusses the design of feedback controllers for bipedal robots, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of virtual constraints and hybrid zero dynamics involves control theory (cs.SY) and mechanical engineering (cs.ME). The paper also mentions the implementation of these techniques on various robots, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV) if the robots are using these technologies.
